00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
&gt;&gt; The story of 2010/2011 season of Beram Kayal in Celtic can be told from the end

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Fans' player of the Year, That was the Skipper for one game was injured twice during the season

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Between all of that he managed to impress Alex Ferguson and Kenny Dalglish and to be Neil Lennon's Favorite 

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:43.000
You can almost forget the loss of The Championship to rangers And the statement from the beginning of the season: "I am not going to be a player for practice"

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:52.000
[Music]

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:56.000
[Applause]

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:05.000
&gt;&gt; My first game in the Europea league game and I Am in the starting lineup in Celtic Park.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:09.000
It gave me Shivers, 60,000 spectators.

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:16.000
In the Second minute I Tackled good and I saw Neil Lennon is cheering me. It started here.

